<h2 class="bold font-l">Stan Gets Stocked</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
For acting up on Pioneer Day, Grunkle Stan gets put in &quot;ye stocks&quot; and gets tomatoes thrown at him by Li'l Gideon. </p>
</div>
